e cats required urgent treatment due to prolonged smoke exposure. To date, =
I have not received either reimbursement or any response regarding this cla=
im.

Furthermore, I currently require temporary storage for the furniture that w=
as salvaged, as I do not yet have a permanent place to keep these items.

