</head>
<body lang=3D"EN-NZ" link=3D"blue" vlink=3D"purple" style=3D"word-wrap:brea=
k-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Good Afte=
rnoon Raffaella,
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">I have re=
quested payment is made to you today for the Temporary Accommodation.<o:p><=
/o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">For the V=
et Fees, these are not covered by your policy as your cat was not injured a=
s a result of an accident with a motor vehicle as required by the policy.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-left:36.0pt"><b><i><span style=3D"co=
lor:#001272;mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Veterinary fees for your domestic p=
et
<o:p></o:p></span></i></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-left:36.0pt"><i><span style=3D"color=
:#001272;mso-fareast-language:EN-US">We=E2=80=99ll pay for veterinary fees =
if your domestic pet is injured in an accident with a motor vehicle.
<o:p></o:p></span></i></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-left:36.0pt"><i><span style=3D"color=
:#001272;mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Any claim under this benefit will be e=
xcess-free.
<o:p></o:p></span></i></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-left:36.0pt"><i><span style=3D"color=
:#001272;mso-fareast-language:EN-US">We pay this benefit in addition to you=
r contents sum insured.
<o:p></o:p></span></i></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-left:36.0pt"><i><span style=3D"color=
:#001272;mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></i></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-left:36.0pt"><b><i><span style=3D"co=
lor:#001272;mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Limit
<o:p></o:p></span></i></b></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal" style=3D"margin-left:36.0pt"><i><span style=3D"color=
:#001272;mso-fareast-language:EN-US">We=E2=80=99ll pay up to $500 for each =
event<o:p></o:p></span></i></p>
