<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I ho=
pe you are well this morning.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size=
:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbs=
p;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You =
will receive the $9,000 temporary accommodation payment in 3 to 5 working d=
ays.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></spa=
n></p>
