<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbs=
p;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The =
remaining amount under the temporary accommodation benefit is $13,820.62</s=
pan><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbs=
p;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Is t=
here a time I can contact you this week by phone to finalize your contents =
claim? the loss schedule provided by Asset Restore to date exceeds your sum=
 insured, which means that the contents
 is a total loss as the total value of the contents damaged or destroyed is=
 greater then the sum insured. I work until 1:30 so let me know when this w=
eek suits you.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p><=
/o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbs=
p;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I ha=
ve confirmation that your privacy request and the information you requested=
 was emailed to you on the 25/07/25. If you can check this date and let me =
know if you have it.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt">=
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbs=
p;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Rega=
rding updates, I am more then happy to update you on the first of each mont=
h, would you prefer monthly contacts from me instead of fortnightly?</span>=
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbs=
p;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Rega=
rding further claim files, we can send you assessor reports as we receive t=
hese from the assessor. It would be less prudent for us to resend you the e=
ntire claim file each month and not efficient
 for us due to the time it takes to action these we may end up getting asse=
ssor reports during this process which means that report may not be added t=
o that privacy request.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0p=
t"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbs=
p;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Futu=
re assessor reports should be the only documents we have that you are not g=
iven by the assessor as this would come from us.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"=
 style=3D"font-size:10.0pt"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
